# Cursor ‚Äî WFC Integration

## WFC Skills

WFC skills are installed at `~/.cursor/skills/wfc-*/`. Invoke via slash commands.

### Usage

- `/wfc-review` ‚Äî Run 5-agent consensus code review
- `/wfc-build "feature"` ‚Äî Quick feature with TDD
- `/wfc-plan` ‚Äî Create structured task breakdown
- `/wfc-implement` ‚Äî Execute tasks with parallel agents
- `/wfc-security` ‚Äî STRIDE threat modeling

